#. <section class="sutta" id="sn2.16"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn2.16:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 2"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 2"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn2.16:0.2"
msgid "2. Anāthapiṇḍikavagga"
msgstr "2. With Anāthapiṇḍika"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn2.16:0.3"
msgid "16. Vāsudattasutta"
msgstr "16. With Vāsudatta"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.16:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho vāsudatto devaputto bhagavato santike imaṃ gāthaṃ abhāsi:"
msgstr ""
"Standing to one side, the god Vāsudatta recited this verse in the Buddha’s "
"presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.16:2.1"
msgid "“Sattiyā viya omaṭṭho,"
msgstr "“Like they’re struck by a sword,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: ḍayhamānova → ḍayhamāneva (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn2.16:2.2"
msgid "ḍayhamānova matthake;"
msgstr "like their head was on fire,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.16:2.3"
msgid "Kāmarāgappahānāya,"
msgstr "a mendicant should go forth mindfully,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.16:2.4"
msgid "sato bhikkhu paribbaje”ti."
msgstr "to give up sensual desire.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn2.16:3.1"
msgid "“Sattiyā viya omaṭṭho,"
msgstr "“Like they’re struck by a sword,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.16:3.2"
msgid "ḍayhamānova matthake;"
msgstr "like their head was on fire,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.16:3.3"
msgid "Sakkāyadiṭṭhippahānāya,"
msgstr "a mendicant should go forth mindfully,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn2.16:3.4"
msgid "sato bhikkhu paribbaje”ti."
msgstr "to give up identity view.”"
